name: DITNU Zip Up
description: The most common relative directions are left, right, forward, backward, up, and down. No absolute direction corresponds to any of the relative directions. This is a consequence of the translational invariance of the laws of physics: nature, loosely speaking, behaves the same no matter what direction one moves. As demonstrated by the Michelson-Morley null result, there is no absolute inertial frame of reference.

name: Jonestown Massacre Button Down
description: Jonestown gained lasting international notoriety in 1978, when nearly its whole population died in a mass murder-and-suicide ordered by Jim Jones, the cult leader that founded and ran the town. Jones himself was among the slain, numbering somewhat over nine hundred men, women and children.
